about.summary: A Coffescript Object Notation (CSON) parser for Python 2 and Python 3.

name: cson
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "cson" %}
{% set version = "0.8" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ee8c0166fcd1f51789887197e3e8354ac7befa396fc29706bceb5af25edc9e01

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - speg

test:
  imports:
    - cson

about:
  home: https://github.com/avakar/pycson
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  summary: 'A Coffescript Object Notation (CSON) parser for Python 2 and Python 3.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dfroger
